content:
Ninnudayon Daivam-garddabhameriyathaayu
Chonnathu niraveri- skariyaa sthuthi cheyka.
/tnibiyanmaar mumpil-shleehanmaar pimpil
/tooshaanaddhvaniyaal-baalanmaaraartthu.
Skariyaa munchonnu-sehyonputhree! Nee
Thoshichaalum nin-raajaavaagathanaayu
/tkuttikallooshaanaa-aartthupukazhnnone
/tmashihaa! Ee sthuthiyaal-krpa cheytheedenam
